article_title: The Biggest Loser In The Democratic Debate Wasn't Hillary Or Bernie, It Was Obamacare

article_metadata.description: The Clinton-Sanders spat shows that not even Democrats like the Affordable Care Act much, and that the law remains very much in danger of repeal.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
